# ─── Unreal Engine build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────
Binaries/
Build/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.sdf
*.sln
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.xcodeproj/
*.xcworkspace/
.vs/

# ─── IDE / editor config ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# ─── OS cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
